  "text": "For screening purposes, LPS was obtained after proteinase K digestion of whole cells [CITATION_1] . LPS samples were separated by sodium dodecyl sulfate-polyacrylamide gel electrophoresis (SDS-PAGE) or Tricine (N-[2-hydroxy-1,1-bis(hydroxymethyl)ethyl]glycine)-SDS-PAGE and visualized by silver staining as previously described [CITATION_2] .",
