      "span_text": "LPS samples were separated by sodium dodecyl sulfate-polyacrylamide gel electrophoresis (SDS-PAGE) or Tricine (N-[2-hydroxy-1,1-bis(hydroxymethyl)ethyl]glycine)-SDS-PAGE and visualized by silver staining as previously described [CITATION_2] ."
